## Design & Experience

The dashboard is modeled after **clean, modern executive dashboards** — dark sidebar, blue accents, white cards, minimal clutter. The goal is for you to open it once in the morning and have everything you need in front of you.

### Polished & Ready
- Dashboard summary cards (Urgent Actions, Calendar, Tasks, Agenda)
- Sidebar navigation with clean icons
- Email page with two-column layout and color-coded priority sections
- Email detail view with draft editing, status buttons, and quick actions
- Search bar for finding any email

### Still Being Refined
- Meeting Agenda page (functional, design in progress)
- Tasks page (redesign planned with categories and collapsible sections)
- Mobile optimization
- Some popup modals

---

## A Few Things to Know

- **Calendar access:** You'll need to share your calendar with the app (one-time setup)
- **Attachments:** You can see attachment info in the dashboard; to download, it links you to Gmail
- **Apps Script:** The email processing runs under your Google account to ensure proper access
- **Hosting:** The app runs on Vercel with Supabase as the database — secure, fast, and reliable

